title: Norm And Abnormal Norman - Best Of For Now - [mp3 320]
description:
Norm And Abnormal Norman was formed in 2014 by Lige Williamson and Kyle Stersic in Boulder CO, but have since then relocated to Brooklyn NY. They play and compose in a variety of styles centered around blues, jazz, country, folk, singer-songwriter, and avant-garde.

This is a compilation of recordings from their music video collection, Born Again T.V. and from basement recordings made in Brooklyn, NY with an Akai M8 reel to reel.
